  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Main] Reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. You may play
    any number of Digimon cards with [Mamemon] in their names whose play costs add
    up to 15 or less among them without paying their memory costs. Delete 1 of your
    opponent''s Digimon with a memory cost of 6 or less for each Digimon played with
    this effect. Trash the remaining cards.'
